snippet.title: Pyre - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Lead your band of exiles to freedom in this party-based RPG from the creators of Bastion and Transistor.
Steam:  http://goo.gl/VGJMDN  | PS4: https://goo.gl/wo36aq

Music: "Will of the Scribes" from the Pyre Original Soundtrack.

More at: http://www.supergiantgames.com | @SupergiantGames
